v1.0.0
  - Added travis ci integration
  - Added scons build files
  - Added README
  - Added tests/test.cpp as source for unit testing and code coverage
  - Added include/x as header and implementation
  - Added bump-version script to manage version in README and header
  - Added setTimeout(function, instance, ticks) for static functions
  - Added setTimeout<T, f>(instance, ticks) for member functions
  - Added setup(void) as optional initializer
  - Added loop(ticks) with binary heap as backend
